===Load/Store Instructions=== {| |''Instruction''||''Description'' |- | colspan="2" style="border-top:1px solid grey;" | |- |LDA||Load accumulator from memory |- |LDX||Load register X from memory |- |LDY||Load register Y from memory |- |STA||Store accumulator in memory |- |STX||Store register X in memory |- |STY||Store register Y in memory |- |STZ||Store zero in memory |}
